metadata.name: Seven of Cups
metadata.description:
The Seven of Cups - Tap into abundance

This card symbolises an abundance of choices, options and opportunities.  The card depicts a person with her back turned away, contemplating a myriad of fantastical dreams and fortunes, meditating over the options ahead, tapping into cosmic energy and abundance and trying to recenter.

If you find yourself at a crossroad or in the face of choices, this will be your token to tap into abundance.

Ethereal Journey Tarot is a collaborative deck where each card is individually designed by a different international artist.
